ire, Schottland, United Kingdom begraben."},"ht":{"1370–1392":"1370–1392","1355–1407":"1355–1407","1387–1438":"1387–1438","1388–1419":"1388–1419","1325–1400":"1325–1400","1325":"1325","1400":"1400","1388":"1388","1355":"1355","1387":"1387","1382":"1382","1370":"1370","1392":"1392","1419":"1419","1407":"1407","1438":"1438","Nithsdale, Dumfriesshire, Scotland":"Dumfriesshire, Scotland","Danzig, Poland":"Gdańsk, pomorskie, Pologne","Scotland":"Scotland","Ayrshire, Scotland":"Ayrshire, Ecosse, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"1370–1392":"1370–1392","1355–1407":"1355–1407","1387–1438":"1387–1438","1388–1419":"1388–1419","1325–1400":"1325–1400","1325":"1325","1400":"1400","1388":"1388","1355":"1355","1387":"1387","1382":"1382","1370":"1370","1392":"1392","1419":"1419","1407":"1407","1438":"1438","Nithsdale, Dumfriesshire, Scotland":"Dumfriesshire, Scotland","Danzig, Poland":"Gdańsk, pomorskie, Lengyelország","Scotland":"Scotland","Ayrshire, Scotland":"Ayrshire, Skócia, United Kingdom"},"id":{"1370–1392":"1370–1392","1355–1407":"1355–1407","1387–1438":"1387–1438","1388–1419":"1388–1419","1325–1400":"1325–1400","1325":"1325","1400":"1400","1388":"1388","1355":"1355","1387":"1387","1382":"1382","1370":"1370","1392":"1392","1419":"1419","1407":"1407","1438":"1438","Nithsdale, Dumfriesshire, Scotland":"Dumfriesshire, Scotland","Danzig, Poland":"Gdańsk, pomorskie, Polandia","Scotland":"Scotland","Ayrshire, Scotland":"Ayrshire, Skotlandia, United Kingdom"},"it":{"1370–1392":"1370–1392","1355–1407":"1355–1407","1387–1438":"1387–1438","1388–1419":"1388–1419","1325–1400":"1325–1400","1325":"1325","1400":"1400","1388":"1388","1355":"1355","1387":"1387","1382":"1382","1370":"1370","1392":"1392","1419":"1419","1407":"1407","1438":"1438","Nithsdale, Dumfriesshire, Scotland":"Dumfriesshire, Scotland","Danzig, Poland":"Gdańsk, pomorskie, Polonia","Scotland":"Scotland","Ayrshire, Scotland":"Ayrshire, Scozia, Regno Unito","lifeSummary":"Sir William Douglas Lord Nithsdale è nato il nel 1370 nel Dumf